comment.body:
The only thing is that you probably copy pasted the wrong strings when writing the build_config.

```
"attribute_filter": {
                "attribute_filter": "Attribute Filter",
                "field_type": "code",
            },
```
Should probably be:
```
"attribute_filter": {
                "display_name": "Attribute Filter",
                "field_type": "code",
            },
```
